Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the Buca di Beppo Capri room reveal, the return of Brandi and Kim, and more! On The Real Housewives of New York, the women return to the city for cabaret rehearsal and Sonja's clothing party.


RHONY Recap: 22:54ish
